  "title": "fix(dependencies): remove qs limitation",
  "body": "Previously, we limited qs to versions < 6.10, because since that version the size of the package significantly increased (~10kb).\r\n\r\nHowever, a vulnerability (https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-6rw7-vpxm-498p) relevant for server use cases causes us to need to bump the version past 6.14.1 allowed now.\r\n\r\nFixes #6849",
